1372
01:16:17,956 --> 01:16:21,193
<font face="Serif" size="18">They also served in Burundi for eight years.</font>

1373
01:16:21,193 --> 01:16:23,962
<font face="Serif" size="18">Presently, they serve in Ghana,</font>

1374
01:16:23,962 --> 01:16:28,567
<font face="Serif" size="18">where Brother Jones serves
