1376
01:16:32,104 --> 01:16:34,806
<font face="Serif" size="18">because their class was highlighted</font>

1377
01:16:34,806 --> 01:16:38,377
<font face="Serif" size="18">in the video <i>To the Ends of the Earth,</i></font>

1378
01:16:38,377 --> 01:16:40,679
<font face="Serif" size="18">which marked the 50th anniversary</font>

1379
01:16:40,679 --> 01:16:43,682
<font face="Serif" size="18">of the Watchtower Bible School of Gilead.</font>

1380
01:16:43,682 --> 01:16:48,120
<font face="Serif" size="18">It was a very enlightening video for sure.</font>

1381
01:16:48,120 --> 01:16:51,456
<font face="Serif" size="18">Although the purpose
of Gilead School training</font>

1382
01:16:51,456 --> 01:16:53,892
<font face="Serif" size="18">has changed since then,</font>

1383
01:16:53,892 --> 01:16:57,396
<font face="Serif" size="18">it’s clear from their heartfelt comments</font>

1384
01:16:57,396 --> 01:17:02,167
<font face="Serif" size="18">that they’ve proven to be
a stabilizing and strengthening influence</font>

1385
01:17:02,167 --> 01:17:04,169
<font face="Serif" size="18">where they have served.</font>

1386
01:17:04,169 --> 01:17:06,204
<font face="Serif" size="18">So enjoy the video.</font>

1387
01:17:09,775 --> 01:17:12,244
<font face="Serif" size="18">This is the day when we hand out assignments</font>

1388
01:17:12,244 --> 01:17:13,912
<font face="Serif" size="18">to all of these students.</font>

1389
01:17:13,912 --> 01:17:15,914
<font face="Serif" size="18">The morning that we knew
we were going to get our assignment,</font>

1390
01:17:15,914 --> 01:17:17,949
<font face="Serif" size="18">we went down to morning worship,</font>

1391
01:17:17,949 --> 01:17:21,853
<font face="Serif" size="18">and then we had to line up,
and we were waiting to get our assignment.</font>

1392
01:17:21,853 --> 01:17:25,524
<font face="Serif" size="18">And my stomach was churning,
and I felt really sick</font>

1393
01:17:25,524 --> 01:17:28,860
<font face="Serif" size="18">—sick with excitement
as well as the fact that you knew</font>

1394
01:17:28,860 --> 01:17:30,762
<font face="Serif" size="18">that whatever Brother Jaracz said,</font>

1395
01:17:30,762 --> 01:17:32,998
<font face="Serif" size="18">the next sentence that came out of his mouth</font>

1396
01:17:32,998 --> 01:17:35,233
<font face="Serif" size="18">would determine the rest of your life.</font>

1397
01:17:36,802 --> 01:17:38,337
<font face="Serif" size="18">It’s hard to imagine</font>

1398
01:17:38,337 --> 01:17:40,305
<font face="Serif" size="18">that 28 years have gone by</font>

1399
01:17:40,305 --> 01:17:41,873
<font face="Serif" size="18">since our initial assignment.</font>

1400
01:17:41,873 --> 01:17:44,076
<font face="Serif" size="18">But Gilead training really helped us</font>

1401
01:17:44,076 --> 01:17:45,677
<font face="Serif" size="18">to understand that things</font>

1402
01:17:45,677 --> 01:17:46,845
<font face="Serif" size="18">wouldn’t always be easy.</font>

1403
01:17:47,379 --> 01:17:49,147
<font face="Serif" size="18">And that when things weren’t easy,</font>

1404
01:17:49,147 --> 01:17:51,450
<font face="Serif" size="18">we should never overreact to situations</font>

1405
01:17:51,450 --> 01:17:53,885
<font face="Serif" size="18">but keep calm and trust in Jehovah.</font>

1406
01:17:53,885 --> 01:17:57,222
<font face="Serif" size="18">I think one of the outstanding sections
of Gilead for me</font>

1407
01:17:57,222 --> 01:18:01,059
<font face="Serif" size="18">was the section dealing with
